author: Yes Theory
description:
Hi friends, for those of you wish to rep the message and support us telling our stories here on YouTube, our new Seek Discomfort Holiday drop is live now! https://www.seekdiscomfort.com/

LISTEN TO OUR PODCAST! @yestheorypodcast We just recorded a new episode about this experience here: https://youtu.be/gi6j9g7xPdc


Thank you to all the people who helped enable this trip to Pagan despite our setbacks in this story, it turned out to be one hell of adventure. Thank you to the Mariana's Visitors Authority for helping us find the shipping vessel. A special thank you to Mario for showing us his homeland and to Vlad for keeping us safe and taken care of. You can follow Vlad's wild adventure on his Instagram here: https://www.instagram.com/vladimiller_9/

Thank you to @CorySMartin for capturing with grace yet another adventure and for being the best adventure partner.

Who are we? 
We believe life’s greatest moments and deepest connections exist outside your comfort zone.

🙏🏼 Thank you for
title: Stranded on a Deserted Island for 42 Hours (boat engine died)
